title: The Eye Improvement System Home Video
description: The Eye Improvement System Home Video. Devised and perfected by leading specialists in the field of eye care and sports medicine. A series of four highly successful video exercises designed to improve your life through better use of your visual skills. The E.I.S. requires only 15 minutes a day, just 3 times a week. The simple exercises are designed to make improving your eyesight easy and enjoyable in the privacy of your home or office at your convenience. A guarantteed way to: (1.) React Quicker to Danger. (2.) Reduce Chance of Driving Accidents. (3.) Perform Better in Sports. (4.) Guard Against Eye Strain and Fatigue. (5.) Maximize your Job Efficiency. (6.) Improve your Study Skills and Increase Reading Comprehension. This technique has been used effectively by noted sports figures, major corporations, educaters, the military and senior citizen organizations. Distributed by G.M.Z. Productions Inc., New York.
